      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "関係各所と調整して、三枝さんからも許可をもらった\nこれでトリエルの活動休止は正式に決定だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After coordinating with all relevant parties and receiving permission from Saegusa-san\nNow‚ TRINITYAiLE's activities have been officially suspended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達のわがままを聞いてくれて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for listening to\nour selfish request",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "礼を言うのはまだ早いぞ\nさすがに今すぐ活動休止とはいかないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too early to thank you\nNo matter what‚ you can't stop activities right away",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "分かっています。すでに受けた仕事はきちんとやります\n休止するのは、今の仕事が一段落してからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. I'll do my best to fulfill the task I have already accpeted\nStop activities‚ begins when the current work is completed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "と言っても、星見プロみんなが手伝ってくれることに\nなったから、それほど時間はかからないと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That said‚ everyone at Hoshimi Prods. is helping out‚\nso I don't think it will take that long",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？\n……みんなにもちゃんとお礼を言わないといけませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?\n…I really need to thank everyone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0831061841,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.66666670000296,
          "startTime": 43.2497728508
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 49.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……事務所に来ていたのね\n会いたいと思っていたからちょうど良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… you were at the office\nI've been wanting to see you‚ so this is a good chance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の代役を引き受けてくれたそうね\n迷惑を掛けてごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you agreed to fill in for us\nSorry for the inconvenience",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、それは大丈夫だけど……\n本当に活動休止するんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm‚ that's fine…\nYou're really going to stop your activities",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.831291787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに寂しそうな顔しないで\n引退する訳でも、星見プロを辞める訳でもないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't make a sad face\nWe're not retiring or quitting Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "私達はすぐに帰ってくるわ\nサニピよりも強くなってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll be back soon\nBe stronger than Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "むぅ……\n私達だって負けないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm…\nWe won't lose either~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4452371439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃん。何かあったらみんなや\n{user}さんにすぐ連絡してね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan. If anything happens‚ please contact everyone or\n{user}-san right away",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4785689514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "事務所にも、いつでも来ていいんだからな\n星見プロは君達の家なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can come to the office‚ anytime\nHoshimi Prods. is like your home",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8766188782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、私はそろそろ行きます\n優やすみれとこれからのことを話し合わないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I'll be going soon\nI have to discuss our future plans with Yu and Sumire",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5966.666666600006,
          "startTime": 109.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……またね、さくら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…See you‚ Sakura",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8054606757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 110.8038516921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエル、本当に活動休止するんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE‚ they're really going to stop",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8038516921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんが休止を決めたのは\nライブバトルで私達に負けたから……なんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason Rui-chan decided to stop was\nbecause she lost to us in the live battle… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4038516921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "だったら私達には、トリエルの分まで頑張る責任が\nありますね。トリエルが帰ってくるまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ we have a responsibility to do our best for\nTRINITYAiLE. Until TRINITYAiLE returns…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2933869986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、トリエルが帰ってきても、BIG4らしく\n頂点に立つアイドルとして勝ち続けないと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ even after TRINITYAiLE returns‚ we have to keep winning\nas the idols who stand at the top like BIG4…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1371850254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（勝利を誓うさくらの意志は立派なもので）\n（水を差すようなことではないが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura's determination to win is admirable）\n（I didn't mean to putting a damper on her…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（なぜだろう、勝ちにこだわるさくらを見ていると）\n（胸がざわついてくるのは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Why is it‚ when I see Sakura obsessed with winning）\n（my heart feels heavy…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.376549713,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1300.0000000000114,
          "startTime": 154.676549713
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 154.676549713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、ありがとう！　みんなの声援から力をもらって\n今日のライブバトルも勝つことが出来ました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ everyone! Your cheers gave me power‚\nand I was able to win today's live battle!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9098830463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.2432092589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_05-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが最高の笑顔になれるように\nこれからも頑張るからねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll do my best so that\neveryone can have the best smileー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.5098830463,
